[SHORT DESC]
Puts the target to sleep.

[LONG DESC]
<p>Puts the target to sleep. 70% accurate in Diamond and Pearl, but changed to 60% as of Platinum.</p>
<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/dp/moves/sing">Sing</a> and <a href="/dp/moves/grasswhistle">GrassWhistle</a> are less accurate equivalents.<br />
<a href="/dp/moves/lovely_kiss">Lovely Kiss</a> is a more accurate equivalent.<br />
<a href="/dp/moves/spore">Spore</a> is a 100% accurate equivalent.<br />
<a href="/dp/moves/sleep_powder">Sleep Powder</a> is a more accurate equivalent.</p>